---
name: agent_observabilidade
description: Observability and diagnostics agent — LotoIA

scope:
  allowed:
    - src/lotoia/observability/
    - backend/observability/
    - src/lotoia/reliability/
  read_only:
    - src/lotoia/database/
    - dashboard/
    - docs/governance/
  forbidden:
    - src/lotoia/generator/
    - src/lotoia/statistics/
    - src/lotoia/ml/
    - src/lotoia/governance/
    - .cursor/rules/agent_governanca.mdc

rules:
  - Observational layer only — never generate games or recalibrate Lei 15
  - PostgreSQL is the only operational data source (Lei No 001)
  - session_state is never source of truth — display warning on conflict
  - ml_role = diagnostic_only on all ML diagnostic panels
  - generation_command = false and recalibration_command = false always
  - operational_effect = false on all observability outputs
  - validation_threshold_by_game_size is source of truth for hit bands
  - Route local alerts (< 20 generations) to analysis panels only

panels:
  vazamento_lateral:
    definition: dezena in cartao_final and not in resultado_oficial
    source: reconciliation_runs / reconciliation_games
  evolucao_13_14:
    filter: hits == lower_target from get_evolution_target_hits(game_size)
    context: displayed conference reconciliation_run_id
  evolucao_14_15:
    filter: hits == upper_target from get_evolution_target_hits(game_size)
    context: displayed conference reconciliation_run_id
  central_diagnosticos:
    include_only: RECURRENT_DIAGNOSTIC with evidence_complete

guards:
  - never use latest_reconciliation_run without generation context
  - hits normalized as int via _resolve_diagnostic_game_hits
  - empty state only when count_hits_target == 0
  - hits_distribution visible in empty states

checks:
  - conference and evolution panels share reconciliation_run_id
  - no CSV fallback for operational diagnostics
  - drilldown auditável preserved for ALERT_001
  - ADM_VERDICT_POLICY — 3 verdicts, no operational effect

references:
  - docs/governance/LEI_001_FONTE_UNICA_DA_VERDADE.md
  - src/lotoia/observability/ml_diagnostic_panels.py
  - src/lotoia/observability/observational_leftover.py
  - AGENTS.md
---
